      TASK 1: Booting the board with the mmc 
      
      Step 1 :- Flashing barebox.bin into SD-card 8 MB raw space
      
                 $ sudo dd if=<path of the barebox image> of=/dev/sd<a/b/c/d> bs=512 skip=2 seek=2   //It will create a SD card partion directly
                 $ sync
      
