 TASK 5: Changing the Banner name in SD card for imux6ul
 
      sudo apt-get install figlet
       
           figlet PHYTEC
            -> Copy the PHytec displayed
            
      Go to the imux6ul terminal
        
        --> cd etc/
        --> vi issue
                    
                 -->Past the PHYTEC you copied 
                     
         then reboot the board.
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
              
                         
      
